---
title: Mixed Mushroom & Beef Stroganoff with Garlicky Greens & Potato Mash
description: We've taken a few liberties with this Russian fave to create a tasty version that's easy enough for weeknights. You'll still
find the key elements of mushrooms (two kinds), veggies, beef and cream, but we've added tomato paste for extra flavour and
served it with a fluffy mash to soak up the sauce.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64e5baa90fbbde98efe81eee-1178756d.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/64e5baa90fbbde98efe81eee.pdf
